 elementskit-section-title \">Returns &amp; Refund Policy<\/h2><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a01c8d1 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a01c8d1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5432b7a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5432b7a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-417fef0 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"417fef0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;slideInUp&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:100}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_left   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h2 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Returns &amp; Refund Policy<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<div class='ekit-heading__description'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>At <strong>Shila Vive<\/strong>, customer satisfaction is our priority.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Returns Eligibility<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Returns are accepted only if:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>The product is damaged or defective at the time of delivery<\/p>\n<p>Wrong product was delivered<\/p>\n<p><strong>Return Request Timeline<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Customers must raise a return request within 7 days of delivery.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Non-Returnable Items<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Returns will not be accepted if:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Product is opened or used<\/p>\n<p>Damage is caused after delivery<\/p>\n<p>Request is raised after the return window<\/p>\n<p><strong>Refund Process<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Refunds are initiated only after inspection and approval.<\/p>\n<p>Refunds will be processed through the same payment method used during purchase.<br \/>(As per Razorpay policy: refunds are routed back to the original payment source.)<\/p>\n<p><strong>Refund Timeline<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Refunds are usually completed within 5\u201310 business days after approval.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Chargebacks<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Customers are encouraged to contact us first before raising disputes, as chargebacks may require additional verification.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Returns &amp; Refund Policy Returns &amp; Refund Policy At Shila Vive, customer satisfaction is our priority. Returns Eligibility Returns are<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-9050","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/9050","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=9050"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/9050\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9054,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/9050\/revisions\/9054"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=9050"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}